chevron lubricants lanka plc private company information  bloomberg august    am et chemicals company overview of chevron lubricants lanka plc snapshot people company overview chevron lubricants lanka plc engages in blending manufacturing importing distributing and marketing lubricant oils greases brake fluids and specialty products in sri lanka the company offers passenger vehicle four stroke motor cycle two stroke and outboard diesel vehicle and marine engine oils and general purpose automotive gear oils automatic transmission oils industrial lubricants coolants and other products under the havoline delo and caltex brands it also provides inservice oil monitoring systematic failure analysis expertise seminar plant and lab visit lubrication survey drain interval optimization product bulletinguideother publication and endoscope inspec chevron lubricants lanka plc engages in blending manufacturing importing distributing and marketing lubricant oils greases brake fluids and specialty products in sri lanka the company offers passenger vehicle four stroke motor cycle two stroke and outboard diesel vehicle and marine engine oils and general purpose automotive gear oils automatic transmission oils industrial lubricants coolants and other products under the havoline delo and caltex brands it also provides inservice oil monitoring systematic failure analysis expertise seminar plant and lab visit lubrication survey drain interval optimization product bulletinguideother publication and endoscope inspection services as well as health environment and safety support services and lube specialist courses channel partner workshops remote thermo meters vehicle clinics and portable test kits the company also exports its products to bangladesh and maldives the company was incorporated in  and is based in colombo sri lanka chevron lubricants lanka plc is a subsidiary of chevron ceylon limited detailed description chevron houseno  galle roadcolombo  sri lankafounded in  employees phone 