rofile of chevron lubricants lanka plc including a general overview of the companys business and key management as well as employee data and location and contact information industrychemical manufacturing sectorbasic materials employees equity typeord chevron lubricants lanka plc is a sri lankabased company engaged in the business of importing blending distributing and marketing of lubricant oils and greases the company offers passenger vehicle engine oils over four stroke motor cycle engine oils two stroke and outboard engine oil general purpose automotive gear oils automatic transmission oils and other under havoline brand the company offers diesel vehicle engine oils marine engine oils industrial lubricants coolants brake fluids and specialties under delo brand it offers various services such as inservice oil monitoring drain interval optimization lube specialist course vehicle clinics workshops for channel partners systematic failure analysis expertise technical data on fuelsfuel analysis plant and lab visits remote thermo meters ir endoscope inspections and lubrication surveys it provides winged oil monitoring services such as lubewatch oil analysis and fastfluid analysis service and trending contact information address no  galle road colombo colombo sri lanka phone  fax  web chevronlk loading top executives name age since title thushari weragoda   laboratory and quality assurance lead sumith hewavitharana   indirect sales manager hilary fernando   lead technical manager thusitha de silva   direct sales manager erande de silva   manager finance and planning wijitha akmeemana   supply chain manager maheshni hamangoda   human resources manager bertram paul   general manager sales upali wijesinghe   logistics manager adikarige mervin anura perera   chief financial officer company secretary executive director honnantharage kishu pradeep kumara gomes   managing director chief executive officer executive director add a comment comment guidelines comment guidelines we